<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink376">
<l>nāṭoṟuṅ kaliḻu meṉṉiṉu miṭainiṉṟu</l>
<l>kāṭupaṭu tīyiṟ kaṉaliyar mātō</l>
<l>nalviṉai neṭunakar kalleṉak kalaṅkap</l>
<l>pūppurai yuṇkaṇ maṭavaraṟ</l>
<l>pōkkiya puṇartta vaṟaṉil pālē</l>
      </lg>
     <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>May virtueless fate that caused my naïve daughter</l>
<l>with flower-like, kohl eyes to leave,</l>
<l>making our high house of good deeds bitterly suffer, </l>
<l>stand in my place, who is crying every day, </l>
<l>and get burned in the forest fire!  </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
